010@HistoryLogProps(
011    opCode = 256,
012    displayName = "Dexcom G6 CGM Data",
013    internalName = "LID_CGM_DATA_GXB",
014    usedByAndroid = true,
015    usedByTidepool = true, // LID_CGM_DATA_GXB
016    usedByTconnectsync = true
017)
018public class DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
019    
020    private int glucoseValueStatusRaw;
021    private GlucoseValueStatus glucoseValueStatus;
022    private int cgmDataTypeRaw;
023    private Set<CgmDataType> cgmDataTypes;
024    private int rate;
025    private int algorithmState;
026    private int rssi;
027    private int currentGlucoseDisplayValue;
028    private long timeStampSeconds;
029    private int egvInfoBitmaskRaw;
030    private Set<EgvInfo> egvInfo;
031    private int interval;
032    
033    public DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog() {}
034    
035    public DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int glucoseValueStatusRaw, int cgmDataTypeRaw, int rate, int algorithmState, int rssi, int currentGlucoseDisplayValue, long timeStampSeconds, int egvInfoBitmask, int interval) {
036        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, glucoseValueStatusRaw, cgmDataTypeRaw, rate, algorithmState, rssi, currentGlucoseDisplayValue, timeStampSeconds, egvInfoBitmask, interval);
037        parse(cargo);
038        
039    }

041    public int typeId() {
042        return 256;
043    }

045/**
046     * TODO: this needs to be checked against the tconnectsync eventparser code since they seem to differ     *     * <br>     *     * <table border="1">
047     * <caption>Parsed fields for DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog:</caption>
048     * <tr><td><code>glucoseValueStatusRaw</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
049     * <tr><td><code>glucoseValueStatus</code></td><td><code>getGlucoseValueStatus()</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>cgmDataTypeRaw</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
051     * <tr><td><code>cgmDataTypes</code></td><td><code>getCgmDataTypes()</code></td></tr>
052     * <tr><td><code>rate</code></td><td><code>raw[13]</code></td></tr>
053     * <tr><td><code>algorithmState</code></td><td><code>raw[14]</code></td></tr>
054     * <tr><td><code>rssi</code></td><td><code>raw[15]</code></td></tr>
055     * <tr><td><code>currentGlucoseDisplayValue</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
056     * <tr><td><code>timeStampSeconds</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
057     * <tr><td><code>egvInfoBitmaskRaw</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
058     * <tr><td><code>egvInfo</code></td><td><code>getEgvInfo()</code></td></tr>
059     * <tr><td><code>interval</code></td><td><code>raw[24]</code></td></tr>
060     * </table>
061     */
062    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
063        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
064        this.cargo = raw;
065        parseBase(raw);
066        this.glucoseValueStatusRaw = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
067        this.glucoseValueStatus = getGlucoseValueStatus();
068        this.cgmDataTypeRaw = raw[12];
069        this.cgmDataTypes = getCgmDataTypes();
070        this.rate = raw[13];
071        this.algorithmState = raw[14];
072        this.rssi = raw[15];
073        this.currentGlucoseDisplayValue = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
074        this.timeStampSeconds = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
075        this.egvInfoBitmaskRaw = Bytes.readShort(raw, 22);
076        this.egvInfo = getEgvInfo();
077        this.interval = raw[24];
078        
079    }

085     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>

088     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
092     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
093     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
094     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
096     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatus) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
097     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatus) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
098     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>(byte) cgmDataType</code></td></tr>
099     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>(byte) rate</code></td></tr>
100     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>(byte) algorithmState</code></td></tr>
101     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>(byte) rssi</code></td></tr>
102     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
103     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
104     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
105     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
106     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
107     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
108     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
109     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
110     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>(byte) interval</code></td></tr>
111     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>(byte) (1)</code></td></tr>
112     * </table>
113     */
114    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int glucoseValueStatus, int cgmDataType, int rate, int algorithmState, int rssi, int currentGlucoseDisplayValue, long timeStampSeconds, int egvInfoBitmask, int interval) {
115        return Bytes.combine(
116            new byte[]{0, 1},
117            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
118            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
119            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatus), 
120            new byte[]{ (byte) cgmDataType }, 
121            new byte[]{ (byte) rate }, 
122            new byte[]{ (byte) algorithmState }, 
123            new byte[]{ (byte) rssi }, 
124            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue), 
125            Bytes.toUint32(timeStampSeconds), 
126            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask), 
127            new byte[]{ (byte) interval },
128            new byte[]{ 1 }); // missing param?
129    }

135    public enum GlucoseValueStatus {
136        NORMAL(0),
137        HIGH(1),
138        LOW(2)
139
140        ;
141        private int id;
142        GlucoseValueStatus(int id) {
143            this.id = id;
144        }
145
146        public static GlucoseValueStatus fromId(int id) {
147            for (GlucoseValueStatus r : values()) {
148                if (r.id == id) {
149                    return r;
150                }
151            }
152            return null;
153        }
154
155        public int getId() {
156            return id;
157        }
158    }
159
160    public GlucoseValueStatus getGlucoseValueStatus() {
161        return GlucoseValueStatus.fromId(glucoseValueStatusRaw);
162    }
163
164    public int getCgmDataTypeRaw() {
165        return cgmDataTypeRaw;
166    }

168    public enum CgmDataType {
169        FIVE_MINUTE_READING(1),
170        BACKFILL(2),
171        IMMEDIATE_MATCH_VALUE(4),
172        CALIBRATION(8),
173        NONE(16)
174
175        ;
176        private int id;
177        CgmDataType(int id) {
178            this.id = id;
179        }
180
181        public static Set<CgmDataType> fromId(int mask) {
182            Set<CgmDataType> items = new TreeSet<>();
183            for (CgmDataType i : values()) {
184                if ((mask & i.getId()) != 0) {
185                    items.add(i);
186                }
187            }
188
189            return items;
190        }
191
192        public int getId() {
193            return id;
194        }
195    }
196
197    public Set<CgmDataType> getCgmDataTypes() {
198        return CgmDataType.fromId(cgmDataTypeRaw);
199    }

237        public static Set<EgvInfo> fromId(int mask) {
238            Set<EgvInfo> items = new TreeSet<>();
239            for (EgvInfo i : values()) {

242                }
